:2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:19:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/02/141818_becdc2b8965669c134d81b706ac14136.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F02%2F141818_becdc2b8965669c134d81b706ac14136.jpg&h=8a6a25a8&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n做乜撚野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528ea8deed0c7e1faf24a3f38f14209a867e3a22","tid":384173,"uid":81737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:22:32.000Z","msg":"WD40 KO"},{"pid":"bb727f3fa9d424ba0972a5caedaaaa2d54e16fcb","tid":384173,"uid":110749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:23:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用蠟捽兩野唔見八成<br />\n成條噴就二千樓下<br />\n<br />\n咁小傷唔使搞啦</blockquote><br />\n蠟 幾錢到？邊到有得整，唔係好識"},{"pid":"d6f9e1006f7c03833128c5b812b0d9dfd963eba8","tid":384173,"uid":84472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:25:46.000Z","msg":"試下買支油筆"},{"pid":"28600238c897a1f8606f6cb03d3ea97cc7f91556","tid":384173,"uid":110749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T07:05:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下買支油筆</blockquote><br />\n係邊會有得買？真無呢方面智識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86afef60d818b3995b3ff5ee4965ccfca7cdaf50","tid":384173,"uid":16772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T07:07:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/02/141818_becdc2b8965669c134d81b706ac14136.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F02%2F141818_becdc2b8965669c134d81b706ac14136.jpg&h=8a6a25a8&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d1fbe555d16cf77404948b42d39241fddfb68f","tid":384173,"uid":73862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:11:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/02/141818_becdc2b8965669c134d81b706ac14136.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F02%2F141818_becdc2b8965669c134d81b706ac14136.jpg&h=8a6a25a8&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n你好叻呀"},{"pid":"c972375f8386ddc9a636cec96229a0556b27aefa","tid":384173,"uid":94591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:36:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用蠟捽兩野唔見八成<br />\n成條噴就二千樓下<br />\n<br />\n咁小傷唔使搞啦</blockquote><br />\n蠟 幾錢到？邊到有得整，唔係好識</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://cbu01.alicdn.com/img/ibank/2010/444/190/215091444_809381960.400x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcbu01.alicdn.com%2Fimg%2Fibank%2F2010%2F444%2F190%2F215091444_809381960.400x400.jpg&h=a230d2be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"911a5274caeeec029311d7c38b65ed2c709ea0c3","tid":384173,"uid":28558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:56:42.000Z","msg":"自己整好考功夫，我以前試過俾貨車拉花hit and run, 傷㾗見骨，但我一來唔想俾錢人賺二來想學多門，就打咗俾朋友個朋友學，佢搞車房<br />\n<br />\n跟住佢教咗我好入門既方法<br />\n1: 買支研磨劑抛一抛佢先，然後摺埋張幼沙紙稍為輕輕整平佢<br />\n2: 確保冇碎屑唔界手後，過一段時間後（大約幾星期，期間有渣車），買返架車既色油<br />\n3: 洗同抹乾後，用一支極細毛筆（騰文嗰種），拎極少油，少於一滴，用點既方法補色，一點一點咁補好佢，補好後用研磨劑再抛一抛佢<br />\n4: 如是者又渣車渣幾星期，幾星期後做返相同動作，目的係點到啲油同表面一樣高度就可以，如果睇你個傷做兩次就夠。<br />\n5: 又渣多個幾星期，到時到候摸摸佢，如果傷痕滑既唔拮手既就ok，太凹補油，太有凸既就研磨劑甚至極細號砂紙整平佢，呢度極technical 如果整開模型會好啲，我由細到大玩開Gunpla<br />\n6: 到滿意又平又滑啦，做埋最後一次研磨，然後勤打粗臘（我用雞雞香蕉臘）幼臘（我用3M)就完成。<br />\n<br />\n慢係慢啲，但補出黎既效果絕對係令任何人都睇唔出你花過，每次工序所需時間都唔長，熟手既，10-15 分鐘而已"},{"pid":"cde5e1a527c6256e78a961b7e5d4b095cf4fd920","tid":384173,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:56:59.000Z","msg":"屌打咗咁撚多字我痴鳩咗"},{"pid":"e0f3e8d678038911fe9ccd0cfee076241741fe99","tid":384173,"uid":16580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:21:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌打咗咁撚多字我痴鳩咗</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁有心支持下"},{"pid":"c68845a90afe5ce97f4931934b2e8059fb95d7c5","tid":384173,"uid":59466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T21:21:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌打咗咁撚多字我痴鳩咗</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁有心支持下</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝分享，支持支持"},{"pid":"3d712b5fa6572bfe8c154a37330da82dddc8a056","tid":384173,"uid":42732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T01:12:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己整好考功夫，我以前試過俾貨車拉花hit and run, 傷㾗見骨，但我一來唔想俾錢人賺二來想學多門，就打咗俾朋友個朋友學，佢搞車房<br />\n<br />\n跟住佢教咗我好入門既方法<br />\n1: 買支研磨劑抛一抛佢先，然後摺埋張幼沙紙稍為輕輕整平佢<br />\n2: 確保冇碎屑唔界手後，過一段時間後（大約幾星期，期間有渣車），買返架車既色油<br />\n3: 洗同抹乾後，用一支極細毛筆（騰文嗰種），拎極少油，少於一滴，用點既方法補色，一點一點咁補好佢，補好後用研磨劑再抛一抛佢<br />\n4: 如是者又渣車渣幾星期，幾星期後做返相同動作，目的係點到啲油同表面一樣高度就可以，如果睇你個傷做兩次就夠。<br />\n5: 又渣多個幾星期，到時到候摸摸佢，如果傷痕滑既唔拮手既就ok，太凹補油，太有凸既就研磨劑甚至極細號砂紙整平佢，呢度極technical 如果整開模型會好啲，我由細到大玩開Gunpla<br />\n6: 到滿意又平又滑啦，做埋最後一次研磨，然後勤打粗臘（我用雞雞香蕉臘）幼臘（我用3M)就完成。<br />\n<br />\n慢係慢啲，但補出黎既效果絕對係令任何人都睇唔出你花過，每次工序所需時間都唔長，熟手既，10-15 分鐘而已</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e369fb5e8e5b8562776b8a490267cdee635a7ed5","tid":384173,"uid":36445,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T01:32:11.000Z","msg":"車愛黎揸既<br />\nhi花左又唔影響部車既性能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁緊張做乜<br />\n<br />\n利申 無車 番工間唔中會因為呢d hi花事故而塞車"},{"pid":"8b1fbfe604f1f7617f2452ec6be44e2ede1c3bf3","tid":38417